{"tid":1719034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"城大取消全校畢業典禮及學院畢業禮","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T05:24:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b4347c2241eedd68c942311901a070b25a3d3d","tid":1719034,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:59:17.000Z","msg":"香港城市大學宣佈，取消原訂在本月16日至12月8日舉行的學院畢業禮及本月23日的全校畢業典禮。<br />\n城大表示，學校以學生及職員的安全為重，由於香港情形急速變化、近期發生暴力的事件及校園被嚴重破壞，舉行畢業禮的場所亦疑似被縱火，校方因此決定取消畢業禮，形容是一個艱難的決定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492093-20191114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492093-20191114.htm&d=7CNMK8%2FfTiCK2iXV1c%2BwrG5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=3c5220c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492093-20191114.htm&h=4d848564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492093-20191114.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7aead3ee916a4fb0bfbe69d2f25f98646b4bd770","tid":1719034,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"核子工程權威郭位教授又可以繼續匿埋研發新核武保衛校園<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b9ddb9d2add7abe12702c49e38149d3950c3f6","tid":1719034,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7aead3ee916a4fb0bfbe69d2f25f98646b4bd770","tid":1719034,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"核子工程權威郭位教授又可以繼續匿埋研發新核武保衛校園<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:09:23.000Z","msg":"郭位已經深潛左入去海底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67269de121926a1ca438b6428f4c99fb519e3441","tid":1719034,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線 ：向外國報告校園情況！<br />\n<a href=\"https://li